    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">There&#039;s one thing all kids look forward to when the Summer season comes around - swimming! Whether you&#039;re going to the beach, an indoor pool, an outdoor pool or a water park, you&#039;ll want to ensure your child has a trusty pair of swimming goggles to protect their eyes when swimming. The Kidplokio swimming goggles feature an easy to use, quick adjust elastic strap that kids can adjust for a perfect fit. This will not only ensure a comfortable fit, but provides a snug seal to keep water out of your little one&#039;s eyes. The plastic goggles come with a soft silicone frame that won&#039;t irritate skin once adjusted properly</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Kidplokio Kids Swimming Goggles Childrens Swim Mask and Carry Case (3 Colors)</h2>\n  <p>There&#039;s one thing all kids look forward to when the Summer season comes around - swimming! Whether you&#039;re going to the beach, an indoor pool, an outdoor pool or a water park, you&#039;ll want to ensure your child has a trusty pair of swimming goggles to protect their eyes when swimming.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>EASY TO USE QUICK ADJUST STRAP - Kids can easily adjust the elastic strap for a perfect fit, which ensures a comfortable, snug seal to keep water out of eyes while swimming</li>\n    <li>FUN VIBRANT COLOR - The super-bright neon yellow colored goggles add a cool look to any kid&#039;s swimwear, and the high-visibility color helps prevent kids from losing their goggles in the pool or at the beach</li>\n    <li>DESIGNED FOR INDOOR/OUTDOOR SWIMMING - Our goggles are designed to be used in both indoor and outdoor pools, and work great at the beach too!</li>\n    <li>SAFE MATERIAL FOR KIDS - Goggles are made of plastic with a soft silicone eye-frame to provide comfort while protecting eyes from fresh or salt water</li>\n    <li>CONVENIENT CARRY CASE - Our goggles come with a matching neon carry case with a lanyard, so kids can wear them around their neck, attach to their backpack or beach bag while not in use!</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/sports_outdoors/12-35894_goggles_ylw_detail_04.jpg\" alt=\"There&#039;s one thing all kids look forward to when the Summer season comes around - swimming\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> KPSGOGNY1</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810058481146</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> 5 in</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The Kidplokio swimming goggles feature an easy to use, quick adjust elastic strap that kids can adjust for a perfect fit. This will not only ensure a comfortable fit, but provides a snug seal to keep water out of your little one&#039;s eyes. The plastic goggles come with a soft silicone frame that won&#039;t irritate skin once adjusted properly.</p>\n  <p>In addition to the goggles, we&#039;ve included a convenient matching carry case to store the goggles in when not in use! It comes with a lanyard so your child can wear them like a necklace, hang from a backpack or beach bag to keep them handy and organized. The vibrant color will add a fun look to any kid&#039;s swimwear! These swimming goggles are a must-have accessory this Summer!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
